{"tid":700184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[煙剷福音]食物及衞生局局長 陳肇始稱稍後再考慮會否徵稅 規管電子煙　","createTime":"2018-06-13T07:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T10:44:54.000Z","uid":188,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b5d7a745a21fb4dc8db7904bb0e8ccff3dc07ea9","tid":700184,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:01:02.000Z","msg":"食物及衞生局向立法會提交文件，建議修例加強規管電子煙。 食物及衞生局局長陳肇始表示，留意到市場上售賣的電子煙，不少成分也有害健康，會考慮加強規管。至於會否就電子煙徵稅，陳肇始指會留待草擬法例時再考慮。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1401478-20180613.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1401478-20180613.htm&d=m9abxLoKsYMdVqo9ZEqPsAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=429456cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1401478-20180613.htm&h=5045db46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1401478-20180613.htm</a></span>"},{"pid":"94b2c2775d891334ec8264427c2d3bb451e1057c","tid":700184,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93655a5ecc87e726cb2918753f66a940a47fd1f4","tid":700184,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:40:55.000Z","msg":"陳肇始做野好撚慢"},{"pid":"040ef3a5106237f5561589fc6d97f32333e2a07a","tid":700184,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:42:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5bf16c350feafe7d9e08810db298279f559a2631","tid":700184,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:53:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e08fd4596ecc8ba98b5403ce539990e627d40a52","tid":700184,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,